// Details for: soundcore-life-q20-headphones (Soundcore Life Q20, model A3025)
// Lab sheet: CV-EB-A3025-001 — §7.5 ELEVATED gold deepen (Wave Adj/Mid EXTRA 3/8).
//   Upgraded from the first protocol-grade bench (~146 lines) that already held
//   Timer+ ANC OFF/ON stopwatches, Kkmoon weight, FNB58 Micro-USB charge, BT
//   walk, and Egypt field ANC notes. This pass adds sibling A/B ladder hygiene
//   vs Q30 / Q45 (and Q20i/Q11i), soft-pouch vs hard-case trade, airline cabin
//   note, speech-band honesty, and Micro-USB-era honesty — WITHOUT inventing
//   new dB / ms / SNR and WITHOUT pasting sibling stopwatch rows as this
//   sample's own numbers. Corrected: physical NC is ON/OFF (green LED), not
//   Q30's Transport/Indoor/Outdoor triad and not Q20i's app Transparency.
//   Any vendor "% noise reduction" / dB figure = vendor-stated only (§11.3 / §14).
// Wave headphones (over-ear). Physics envelope enforced (§8). §7.5 adapted for
//   over-ear / on-ear: A = full-unit weight (no buds/case split); B = playtime
//   ANC OFF + ANC ON; C/E case steps = N/A (no charging case); D/F = Micro-USB
//   full + quick charge on the unit; G = BT range; H = multipoint (FAIL —
//   not supported); I = ANC qualitative only (no anechoic / no invented dB);
//   J = mic qualitative (no SNR); K = codecs via host OS + Soundcore FAQ
//   (no Soundcore App on A3025); L = latency qualitative (no ms).
// Sibling ladder: Q11i (A3005, no ANC) → Life Q20 (A3025, this file — classic
//   hybrid ANC ON/OFF + Micro-USB + soft pouch, no app/multipoint) → Q20i
//   (A3004, USB-C + Transparency + multipoint + soft pouch) → Life Q30
//   (A3028, Transport/Indoor/Outdoor + hard case + app) → Space Q45 (A3040,
//   Adaptive ANC + LDAC + hard case). Sibling files intentionally untouched:
//   soundcore-q11i / q20i / q30 / q45 / space-one.
// CairoVolt is an INDEPENDENT retailer — not an authorized/official distributor.
